data.text:
Randy Quaid Character Information

Gender: Male ♂ Status: Alive Occupation: Actor First mentioned: "Marge Gamer"

Randy Quaid is a former American actor.

History[edit]

Marge stated that her birthday was on the same date as Randy Quaid's, October 1.[1]

When Bart asked Homer why he needed to eat broccoli, Homer stated so he could grow up healthy and strong like Randy Quaid.[2]

When Homer was getting a lot of attention from people, he said that he couldn't stand the adulation, and that it must be what drove Randy Quaid crazy.[3]
